==In media==
Steve Wozniak has been mentioned, represented, or interviewed countless times in media from the founding of Apple to the present. ''[[Wired magazine|Wired]]'' magazine described him as a person of "tolerant, ingenuous self-esteem" who interviews with "a nonstop, singsong voice".<ref name="World According"/>

